<p>The term <b>citizen media</b> refers to forms of <a href="/wiki/Content_(media_and_publishing)" title="Content (media and publishing)">content</a> produced by private citizens who are otherwise not professional <a href="/wiki/Journalist" title="Journalist">journalists</a>. <a href="/wiki/Citizen_journalism" title="Citizen journalism">Citizen journalism</a>, participatory media and democratic media are related principles.</p>
